    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban doctors from making decisions to make do not resuscitate (DNR) orders",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Ban doctors from making decisions not to attempt cardiopulmonary resuscitation. A DNR order should only be put in place by a person themselves or by their family who have the power to do so. Make doctors request a court order to otherwise make a DNR order.",
